rows.label: bf10140100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]*Panting*

rows.label: bf10140100_0015
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]ADLIB breathing

rows.label: bf10140100_0020
rows.name:
Nia! Byakko!
I'm so glad you're-

rows.label: bf10140100_0030
rows.name: ...Why, Rex?

rows.label: bf10140100_0040
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Huh?

rows.label: bf10140100_0050
rows.name: You told us Eden was real.

rows.label: bf10140100_0060
rows.name:
My lady and I traveled all
this way at your behest.

rows.label: bf10140100_0070
rows.name: Master Rex, did you intentionally deceive us?

rows.label: bf10140100_0080
rows.name:
I trusted you, you know...
I came here because I trusted you!

rows.label: bf10140100_0090
rows.name: N-Nia, Byakko, what are you talking about?

rows.label: bf10140100_0100
rows.name: How do you explain this?!

rows.label: bf10140100_0110
rows.name:
Y-you've got it wrong!
I told you, I promised Homura to-

rows.label: bf10140100_0120
rows.name:
Homura?
Oh right, Homura...

rows.label: bf10140100_0130
rows.name:
Homura...Homura, Homura, Homura!
Is that it?

rows.label: bf10140100_0140
rows.name:
You've only got eyes for her!
Get your head out of your arse!

rows.label: bf10140100_0150
rows.name:
Nia, y-you're being weird.
What is going on?

rows.label: bf10140100_0160
rows.name: My lady has given up everything for you...

rows.label: bf10140100_0170
rows.name: Yet still you realize nothing.

rows.label: bf10140100_0180
rows.name: Even now, you cannot see.

rows.label: bf10140100_0190
rows.name:
I've been here all along!
Why won't you realize?!

rows.label: bf10140100_0200
rows.name:
Look!
Just look at me, Rex!
